    <div>
      <a href="/about/james-thornton" class="font-semibold text-gray-900 hover:text-wine-600">James Thornton</a>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Founder & Lead Wine Consultant | WSET Level 3 Award in Wines</p>
